'''[[Kigali Arena]]''' ni ikibuga gisakaye kiri i [[Kigali]] mu [[Rwanda]], gikoreshwa cyane mumikino ya basketball. Yubatswe kandi irangira muri 2019, yakira ibirori bya siporo nibitaramo. Ni ikibuga kinini cyo mu nzu muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba,giherereye iruhande rwa Stade Amahoro . 
