== Ubwubatsi ==
Kubaka  [[Kigali Arena]], ni umushinga wa guverinoma y’u Rwanda binyuze mu kigo gishinzwe imiturire mu Rwanda (RHA) n’ikigo cya Turukiya Summa, byatangiye muri Mutarama 2019. Kubaka iki ikibuga  byakurikiranwaga na RHA.  Ubwubatsi bwakorwaga ku buryo bwihuse, abantu bagera ku 1.000 kugeza 2000 nibo bakoreshwa muri uyu mushinga haba ku manywa na nijoro. Hagati muri [[Kamena]] 2019, ikibuga cyo mu nzu cyari cyuzuye byibuze 70 ku ijana kandi cyari giteganijwe kurangira muri [[Nyakanga]] 2019. 

Ku ya 9 [[Kanama]] 2019, ikibuga cyafunguwe kumugaragaro na [[Perezida wa Repubulika y’u Rwanda|Perezida]]  w’u Rwanda [[Paul Kagame]] ku mukino wa [[Umupira w’agatebo|basketball]] wahuje Patriot BBC na REG BBC. <ref>Kagire, Edmund (September 25, 2019). [https://ktpress.rw/2019/09/now-president-kagame-wishes-kigali-arena-had-20-000-capacity/ "Now President Kagame Wishes Kigali Arena Had 20,000 Capacity"]. KTpress.com. Retrieved May 23, 2021.</ref> <ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Cn6Z02Njtw KIGALI ARENA Official Inauguration | Kigali, 9 August 2019].</ref> Rwanda

Mu 2021, Kigali Arena yakiriye imikino yo gutangiza shampiyona ya Basketball Africa League (i).
