== Ibiranga ==
Kigali Arena ni ikibuga cyiri munzu gifite ubushobozi bwo kwakira abantu 10,000 kigenewe siporo nka basketball, handball, volley ball, na tennis, ndetse nibitaramo ninama.  Iki kibuga cya siporo giherereye hafi ya Sitade Amahoro nini hamwe na Sitade  Amahoro ntoya yakira abantu 2500. 

== Imikino yakiriye ==
Imikino ya mbere ya siporo yabereye kuri Kigali Arena yari Shampiyona y’Abagore y’abatarengeje imyaka 16 FIBA 2019 .  Izakira  kandi AfroBasket 2021 . 

Yakiriye imikino yanyuma ya Shampiyona yigihugu ya Basketball yu Rwanda 2019. <ref>Komugisha, Usher (September 28, 2019). [https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/kigali-arena-breathes-new-life-rwandan-basketball "Kigali Arena breathes new life into Rwandan basketball"]. ''[[The New Times (Rwanda)|The New Times]]''. Retrieved May 23, 2021.</ref> Ikibuga kandi cyakiriye Final yanyuma yigihembwe cyo gutangiza shampiyona ya Basketball Afrika League (BAL). 

